    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for missing people, lost objects, or even help people solve their problems by handing them over their required items. OVERLOOK is hand-drawn, cozy, relaxing, and funny. btw, watch! there might be a cat hidden in bushes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/b658cc3ad8957182edd11be95e20339b.poster.avif?t=1762795849\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/b658cc3ad8957182edd11be95e20339b.webm?t=1762795849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/b658cc3ad8957182edd11be95e20339b.mp4?t=1762795849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Let's hang out and talk </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/1627caf452b0e28e63ff3d0c349e5960.poster.avif?t=1762795849\" width=686 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/1627caf452b0e28e63ff3d0c349e5960.mp4?t=1762795849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OVERLOOK</strong> is a zen game about people and other creatures living their lives in different tiny cute places and the game has got Meditative gameplay, perfect for relaxing in nowadays stressful situations.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/f6319ce3731f3f57a1364f1a872a9410.poster.avif?t=1762795849\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/f6319ce3731f3f57a1364f1a872a9410.webm?t=1762795849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/f6319ce3731f3f57a1364f1a872a9410.mp4?t=1762795849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you could find hidden/ missing objects in the scene by solving mini-puzzles or simply by looking around and finding the object based on the given clues that you have. or you would help people by solving their needs and issues. hand over a cog to the mechanic guy or help to slice an apple using the lumberjack's ax.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/1f21f47469ec342db50099881c4f8f69.poster.avif?t=1762795849\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/1f21f47469ec342db50099881c4f8f69.webm?t=1762795849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/1f21f47469ec342db50099881c4f8f69.mp4?t=1762795849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >or just watching people do their things and just enjoy the relaxing original lo-fi soundtrack of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a satisfying and mysterious world with 50+ delightful hidden surprises to discover with charming hand-drawn animations and unexpected scenarios.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/812c0af3239bc1dfa80c79fce5174c41.poster.avif?t=1762795849\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/812c0af3239bc1dfa80c79fce5174c41.webm?t=1762795849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/812c0af3239bc1dfa80c79fce5174c41.mp4?t=1762795849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >gameplay includes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles by arranging objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >unpack the untold stories<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/f7c57fb12622bfc608c4f184840e3ae0.poster.avif?t=1762795849\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/f7c57fb12622bfc608c4f184840e3ae0.webm?t=1762795849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1780550/extras/f7c57fb12622bfc608c4f184840e3ae0.mp4?t=1762795849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 50+ unique characters/ creatures </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple, joyful, quick-to-solve puzzles, and satisfying game-play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intuitive drag and drop controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original lo-fi Soundtrack </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Environmental storytelling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming all hand-drawn graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cute hand-drawn animations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric sound design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >feel like a hidden helping hand, a God if you will</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mini-scenarios/ pop-culture references/ hidden loot boxes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Funny and playful, great for all ages!</p></li></ul>",
